- The task expects web Google sign-in using Firebase env (`NEXT_PUBLIC_FIREBASE_*`). With this implementation, unless additional correct client IDs are also set (e.g., `EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_WEB_CLIENT_ID` or `GOOGLE_EXPECTED_CLIENT_IDS`), `/auth/google` can fail even for valid sign-ins.
